  "date": "2026-03-25",
  "notes": "<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:\nauto;text-align:center\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Cartographie\ndes risques de corruption - Compte‑rendu d’entretien<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\n\n<table class=\"MsoNormalTable\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n <tbody><tr>\n  <td style=\"border:solid #E6E6E6 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:solid #E6E6E6 .75pt;\n  background:whitesmoke;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;color:black;mso-color-alt:windowtext\">Date\n  de l’interview</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\n  </td>\n  <td style=\"border:solid #E6E6E6 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:solid #E6E6E6 .75pt;\n  padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">25 mars 2026<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n  </td>\n </tr>\n <tr>\n  <td style=\"border:solid #E6E6E6 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:solid #E6E6E6 .75pt;\n  background:whitesmoke;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;color:black;mso-color-alt:windowtext\">Personne\n  interviewée</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\n  </td>\n  <td style=\"border:solid #E6E6E6 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:solid #E6E6E6 .75pt;\n  padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Christophe Mahé<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n  </td>\n </tr>\n <tr>\n  <td style=\"border:solid #E6E6E6 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:solid #E6E6E6 .75pt;\n  background:whitesmoke;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;color:black;mso-color-alt:windowtext\">Fonction</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\n  </td>\n  <td style=\"border:solid #E6E6E6 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:solid #E6E6E6 .75pt;\n  padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">DSI<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n  </td>\n </tr>\n <tr>\n  <td style=\"border:solid #E6E6E6 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:solid #E6E6E6 .75pt;\n  background:whitesmoke;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;color:black;mso-color-alt:windowtext\">Personnes\n  menant l’entretien</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\n  115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\n  </td>\n  <td style=\"border:solid #E6E6E6 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:solid #E6E6E6 .75pt;\n  padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Sandra Lezmi, Karine Diboues<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n  </td>\n </tr>\n</tbody></table>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">1. Présentation du périmètre, des\nresponsabilités et des activités<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\n\n<ul type=\"disc\">\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:\n     11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Département / Fonction</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <ul type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Direction des Systèmes\n      d’Information (DSI) Groupe.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Couverture multi‑sites et\n      internationale.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n </ul>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:\n     11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Taille et organisation de l’équipe</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <ul type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Environ 100 personnes à\n      l’international, dont ~70 collaborateurs internes.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">20 à 30 prestataires par an,\n      selon les projets.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Plusieurs pôles structurants : <o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <ul type=\"square\">\n   <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Infrastructure</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"> : serveurs, réseaux, data\n       centers, téléphonie.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n   <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Support &amp; maintenance\n       applicative</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"> :\n       gestion des applications, interface avec les éditeurs, planification\n       capacitaire, micro‑évolutions.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n   <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Service Desk / Hotline</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"> : support utilisateurs,\n       préparation des postes, interventions sur site.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n   <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Chefferie de projet</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"> : rôle AMOA/AMOE, études et\n       déploiement des projets applicatifs, gestion des évolutions importantes.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n   <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Validation / Qualification SI</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"> : URS, analyses de risques,\n       cahiers de recette, conformité réglementaire, gestion des changements.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n   <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Cybersécurité</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"> : supervision par le RSI,\n       analyse de logs, monitoring interne, détection d’anomalies.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  </ul>\n </ul>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:\n     11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Activités clés &amp; processus opérationnels\n     associés</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <ul type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Gestion des Appels d’offres\n      (avec Achats au‑delà de 20</span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\n      line-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\"> </span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">000 </span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ascii-font-family:Aptos;\n      mso-hansi-font-family:Aptos;mso-bidi-font-family:Aptos\">€</span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">).<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Gestion des contrats et\n      abonnements logiciels.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Projets majeurs : Concerto\n      (post‑Go‑Live réintégré à la DSI), intégration d’Amber Plasma dans les\n      standards du groupe.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Gestion des prestataires\n      récurrents.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Activités soumises à audit\n      (documents de validation et traçabilité SI).<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n </ul>\n</ul>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">2. Tiers identifiés, interactions et\nrisques évoqués<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Tiers internes<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\n\n<ul type=\"disc\">\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:\n     11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Métiers / Directions opérationnelles</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <ul type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Demandes d’outils SI,\n      applications spécifiques, orientations imposées.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Risques associés : <o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <ul type=\"square\">\n   <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Pressions internes pour\n       imposer un fournisseur ou une application hors processus.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n   <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Contournement des processus\n       d’achat ou de sélection.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  </ul>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Contrôles : hiérarchie métier,\n      soutenances, validation croisée DSI/Achats, revue managériale.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n </ul>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:\n     11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Collaborateurs DSI / Administrateurs</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <ul type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Accès privilégiés sur certaines\n      applications.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Risques : <o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <ul type=\"square\">\n   <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Extraction non autorisée de\n       données sensibles.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n   <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Corruption d’un collaborateur\n       pour accéder aux SI.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  </ul>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Contrôles : segmentation des\n      droits d’administration, logs non supprimables, surveillance cyber,\n      détection d’anomalies horaires ou volumétriques.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n </ul>\n</ul>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Tiers externes<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\n\n<ul type=\"disc\">\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:\n     11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Éditeurs &amp; fournisseurs IT</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <ul type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Interactions fréquentes : négociations\n      commerciales et contractuelles, mise en œuvre de la solution, maintenance\n      applicative, évolutions.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Risques identifiés : <o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <ul type=\"square\">\n   <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Fournisseurs poussant\n       certaines solutions via incentives non transparents.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n   <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Risques de corruption ou de\n       conflits d’intérêt au moment de la sélection d’un prestataire.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  </ul>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;line-height:normal;mso-list:\n      l1 level2 lfo3;tab-stops:list 72.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\">Contrôles\n      : implication des Achats, double validation, cahier des charges établi,\n      soutenances, validation hiérarchique.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n </ul>\n</ul>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<ul type=\"disc\">\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:\n     11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Prestataires externes / consultants en régie</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <ul type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Interventions longues ou\n      récurrentes<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Risques : <o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <ul type=\"square\">\n   <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Facturation fictive ou amplifiée.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n   <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Corruption d’un collaborateur\n       pour valider des heures non réalisées.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n   <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Accès étendu aux systèmes :\n       risques sécurité informatique.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  </ul>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Contrôles : <o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <ul type=\"square\">\n   <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Interaction cadrée par un NDA\n       et des contrats.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n   <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Comptes‑rendus d’activité\n       mensuels vérifiés par un manager.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n   <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Ségrégation des tâches :\n       demandeur différent du valideur du bon de commande.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n   <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Audits des prestataires (réalisés\n       par la qualité, DSI).<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n   <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;line-height:normal;mso-list:\n       l1 level3 lfo3;tab-stops:list 108.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\">Accompagnement\n       systématique par un interne, absence de carte blanche.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  </ul>\n </ul>\n</ul>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:0cm;\nmargin-left:18.0pt;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<ul type=\"disc\">\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:\n     11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Agents de sécurité / Prestataires d’accès aux\n     sites</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <ul type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Risque de corruption pour donner\n      l’accès physique aux locaux à un hacker&nbsp;: risque jugé faible (accès\n      restreints, dégâts possibles mais faible capacité d’exploitation SI).<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n </ul>\n</ul>",
